{"id":772169552,"question_id":3,"lang":"javascript","lang_name":"JavaScript","time":"1 year, 11 months","timestamp":1660337291,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"144 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/772169552/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"49.5 MB","code":"/**\n ** Time O(n), Space(1)\n * @param {number{}} map \n * @param {number} prevDupCharIndex \n */\nfunction removePrevValues(map, prevDupCharIndex) {\n  for (let [key, value] of map.entries()) {\n    if (value <= prevDupCharIndex) map.delete(key);\n  }\n}\n\n/**\n * * Time O(n ^ 2), Space O(n)\n * @param {string} s\n * @return {number}\n */\nfunction lengthOfLongestSubstring(s) {\n  let len = 0;\n  let map = new Map();\n\n  for (let i = 0; i < s.length; i++) {\n    if (map.has(s[i])) {\n      let prevDupCharIndex = map.get(s[i]);\n      removePrevValues(map, prevDupCharIndex);\n      map.set(s[i], i);\n    } else {\n      map.set(s[i], i);\n    }\n\n    if (map.size > len) len = map.size;\n  }\n\n  return len;\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
